g. By the end, they should be ready to assist clients through the supported channels.","title":"New Hire Onboarding for Log a Team","transcript":"[BLANK_AUDIO] And it started.Good morning, everyone. How are you all doing?Great, thanks. I'm all good.Thank you all for joining. If you haven't met yet, we have our two newly hired customer care team members.We can and Maria, hi guys, welcome to the team.Thanks, Andrew. It's great to be here.Hi everyone.And T are k from Human Resources is joining us for a brief period of time, hi T are k.Good morning, everyone.I scheduled this meeting to introduce our new team members to our training process. T are k requested to be prepared.part of this meeting because he has some information for you as well. Tara, could you like to begin?>> Sure. Thank you, Angela.So Maria, Ken.Welcome to Log 18.I want to talk to you about some forms.Now you need to fill out before you can begin work.You have received an email last week.with our liability policy.and our confidentiality agreement.The one about you agree not to share any confidential information about our company with any third parties.Have you received it?Yes, I have.I don't think I received that I'm sorry.No problem. I will send it to you today.Once you have the document,Please read it carefully!and sign electronically.There are four places where you will need to insert your initials.And two, where we need your signature.Was signed and saved?Please send a document directly to me.My email address is tar ik. g old as.at mail. ca.That is T- A- R.e- k- dot.G- U\"L- D- D- D- D- D- D.you there at mail. ca.This is very important.because you cannot work until I have to sign document on file.Do you have any questions?No, I'll send it to you this afternoon.Perfect. Thank you.Ken, please send me an email.So I can double check the email address I have in your file.>> Absolutely, thanks.Okay, that's it.Thank you, Angela, for giving me the time.I will leave the meeting now.Have a good day, everyone.M